

Specifications of the tournaments folder and files
**************************************************

xml tournament files uploaded to opengotha/tournaments

The folders are named : yyyymmdd_shrinkedshortname where yyyymmdd is the begin date
The files are named yyyymmddhhmmss_shrinkedshortname.xml where yyyymmddhhmmss is the save date and time

The shortname is shrinked, keeping  "a" through "z", "A" through "Z" and "0" through "9",  ".", "-"
Other characters, including space are deleted.

  

